consult.evalauto.seleccionInfo: Select the employee who you want to consult its evaluation/self evaluation summary
consult.evalauto.explicacion:
Below is a comparison table between employee's self assessment and the final evaluation by its evaluator.
  • If the competency has a green background, it's considered as key to its position. (weight equal to 5).
  • If the competency has a blue background, it's considered important for its position (weight equal to 3).
  • The remaining competencies will have a weight equal to 1.
  • If any competency has a red background, this indicates that the competency is key with weight equal to 5, and the evaluator has selected it to improve/develop/strengthen on the Competencies Resumee's combos.
The employee doesn't have a final evaluation
